split stanfit object into smaller pieces

Source: R/stan_split.R
stan_split.Rd

Split stanfit post-warmup samples into smaller objects to facilitate parallel post processing.

stan_split(object, ncut = 10, inc_warmup = TRUE)

Arguments

object

stanfit
ncut

numeric, number of smaller objects to create, Default: 10
inc_warmup

logical, include warmup in the smaller objects, Default: TRUE

Value

list of stanfits objects

See also

stan_slice

Other utility: stan_names

Examples

rats <- rats_example()

rats%>%
  stan_split(ncut = 4)
